msgid ""
"22 Stillseed, 365 YW\n"
"Excerpt from the journal of Arvith of Maghre\n"
"\n"
"This patron is, of all things, an elf. I never thought I’d befriend one, but "
"he is less arrogant than the rest. Kalenz, he calls himself. He’s seen too "
"much; I can tell that just by meeting his eyes. I think we will have to work "
"for our pay soon.\n"
"\n"
"In the meantime, though, it’s good to relax and enjoy the peace."
msgstr ""
"22 IX, 365 YW\n"
"Extracte del diari d'Arvith de Maghre\n"
"\n"
"Aquest patró és, a més a més, un elf. Mai hauria pensat que me'n faria amic "
"d'un, però és menys arrogant que la resta. Kalenz, es diu. Ha vist massa "
"coses; ho puc dir simplement per la seva mirada. Crec que aviat haurem de "
"guanyar-nos la paga.\n"
"\n"
"Mentrestant, però, és bo relaxar-se i gaudir de la pau."

